                     <title>Abū al-Qāsim Khalaf ibn ʻAbbās al-Zahrāwī, Sefer Shimush</title>
                     <title xml:lang="he">ספר שמוש</title>
                     <note>First part of a two-volume set (Bodleian Library MS. Huntington Donat. 2
                        (ox.ac.uk)) of the Hebrew translation of Taṣrīf li-man ʻajiza ʻan
                        al-taʼlīf.</note>
                     <editor role="trl">Shem Tov ben Isaak, of Tortosa</editor>
                  </msItem>
